These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, november, august, october
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, chess, skydiving, writing
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, turquise, brown, lilac
City: edinburgh, venice, berlin, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, dutch, nigerian, thai
 1. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
 2. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the brazilian##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 4. the dutch is on the right of the brazilian##1
 5. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the brazilian##1
 7. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person who likes brown is the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the nigerian is the person who likes turquise##1
11. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the thai##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Birthday          | november    | august      | june  | october     |
| Hobby         | writing    | skydiving   | card-games | chess      |
| Color   | turquise       | orange | brown     | lilac    |
| City   | colone | venice         | edinburgh  | berlin    |
| Nationality           | nigerian      | thai       | brazilian | dutch |

