.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, wooden, art-deco
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: july, march, february, april
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, r&b
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, baking, collecting, dancing
There are 4 different favourite colors: purple, aquamarine, brown, yellow
 1. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 2. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 3. the person who likes yellow is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 4. the art-deco house is on the far right##1
 5. the modern house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1
 6. the person who likes brown is on the right of the wooden house##1
 7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 8. the person who's hobby is baking is the fan of r&b##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan of indie##1
10. the fan of disco is on the far right##1
11. the wooden house is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| House      | gothic-revival      | modern     | wooden    | art-deco |
| Birthday   | july | march   | february   | april           |
| Music-Genre   | electronic  | r&b     | indie    | disco         |
| Hobby           | dancing         | baking | collecting     | chess        |
| Color         | purple     | yellow  | aquamarine | brown       |

