.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
House: ranch-style, modern, colonial, victorian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, soul, r&b
4 different pets are kept: fish, frog, mouse, rabbit
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, prince, fonseca, dannemann
4 different games are played: canasta, monopoly, go, bridge
 1. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far left##1
 2. the prince-smoker is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the colonial house is the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the modern house is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
 5. the fonseca-smoker is on the right of the victorian house##1
 6. the person playing bridge is the colonial house##1
 7. the fan of soul is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1
 9. the fan of r&b is the owner of the frog##1
10. the fan of electronic is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
11. the person playing bridge is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the colonial house is on the right of the prince-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| House          | ranch-style    | victorian      | colonial  | modern   |
| Music-Genre   | r&b     | soul      | electronic | disco      |
| Pet           | frog       | fish         | rabbit  | mouse         |
| Cigar         | tiparillo | prince | fonseca  | dannemann |
| Game     | go       | canasta         | bridge   | monopoly        |

