.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, crime, animation, horror
There 4 different types of food: garlic, grapefruit, pepper, raspberry
4 different games are played: scrabble, go, poker, snooker
City: liverpool, marseilles, venice, berlin
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, hip-hop, house, r&b
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 2. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
 3. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is on the far right##1
 5. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
 6. the fan of house is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 7. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person playing go is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the far right##1
11. the person watching animation movies is on the far left##1
12. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person eating grapefruit##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | animation   | horror   | crime      | satire     |
| Food          | pepper     | garlic   | raspberry | grapefruit |
| Game   | go | poker | scrabble   | snooker       |
| City           | marseilles       | liverpool      | berlin     | venice |
| Music-Genre     | reggae    | house     | r&b     | hip-hop     |

