.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-5::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, poppy, iris, bellflower
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, rowing, tennis
City: marseilles, san-francisco, berlin, new-york
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate, tea, cola
4 different pets are kept: bird, ferret, lizard, snake
 1. the person traveling to marseilles is the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is the person who growsiris##1
 5. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
 8. the owner of the snake is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 9. the person who growsbellflower is the owner of the lizard##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
12. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left##1
13. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
14. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking cola##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Flower          | daisy       | poppy     | iris     | bellflower  |
| Sport         | rowing  | tennis | lacrosse | handball  |
| City           | san-francisco | marseilles    | new-york    | berlin |
| Beverage   | cola    | tea   | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Pet           | bird       | snake     | ferret     | lizard   |

