City: hannover, liverpool, london, hamburg
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris, dahlia, tulip
 1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the modern house##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 3. the owner of the rabbit is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the wooden house##1
 6. the wooden house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the person who growsdahlia is the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the wooden house##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
10. the person traveling to london is the person who growstulip##1
11. the owner of the turtle is the person watching animation movies##1
12. the modern house is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Pet         | dog   | turtle | rabbit    | hedgehog  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports    | animation | fantasy      | documentary |
| House   | modern | wooden | cape-cod         | townhouse  |
