.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball, basketball, badminton
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, gardening, magic-tricks, skydiving
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, quad-bike, skateboard, motorbike
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, grey, orange, aquamarine
House: victorian, ranch-style, craftsman, cape-cod
 1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the victorian house##1
 2. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who likes blood-red##1
 4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who likes aquamarine##1
 6. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 9. the victorian house is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
11. the person driving the skateboard is the victorian house##1
12. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |      4       |
| Sport          | skiing     | basketball | volleyball  | badminton   |
| Hobby         | skydiving | cooking    | gardening | magic-tricks |
| Transport   | snowmobile | skateboard     | motorbike    | quad-bike         |
| Color   | orange   | blood-red    | grey   | aquamarine    |
| House           | craftsman    | victorian       | cape-cod    | ranch-style        |

