 4. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
 5. the person eating potato is the cottage house##1
 6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person traveling to boston##1
 7. the australian is the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person drinking cola is the person eating garlic##1
 9. the japanese is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
10. the ranch-style house is the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person eating pepper is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
12. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
13. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage    | coffee        | cola       | milk         | hot-chocolate |
| Nationality       | argentine       | australian | japanese      | spanish     |
