The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, accountant, videographer, architect
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, family, scientific, superhero
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, green, lavender, light-blue
There 4 different types of food: garlic, radish, pear, blueberry
 1. the person eating pear is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 2. the person eating garlic is on the left of the videographer##1
 3. the accountant is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 5. the person playing go is the person who likes lavender##1
 6. the person who likes green is on the far right##1
 7. the person eating blueberry is the person playing monopoly##1
 8. the social-worker is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
10. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
11. the accountant is the person playing go##1
12. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Game      | go     | monopoly      | poker    | canasta           |
| Job         | accountant   | videographer  | social-worker  | architect |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | family     | documentary | scientific    |
| Color   | lavender      | light-blue     | coral  | green         |
| Food         | garlic | blueberry | radish    | pear       |

