 3. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the person eating orange is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 5. the person playing whist is on the far right##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is on the far left##1
 7. the security-guard is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
 8. the person playing canasta is on the right of the fisherman##1
 9. the person eating orange is the person playing chess##1
10. the person eating peas is the person watching action movies##1
11. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
12. the person eating peasmelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |       2        |      3      |      4       |
| Food    | orange     | blueberry  | peas       | peasmelon      |
| Flower       | sunflower    | begonia        | tulip  | iris      |
| Job         | fisherman  | security-guard | firefighter | photographer |
| Movie-Genre         | thriller | drama          | action         | zombie      |
| Game   | chess     | canasta     | backgammon       | whist          |

