.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda, sprite, water
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, train, quad-bike
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, july, december
City: berlin, prague, nizza, paris
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, lavender, turquise, purple
 1. the person traveling to nizza is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking mirinda is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 3. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes white##1
 4. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to berlin##1
 5. the person driving the train is the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person drinking water##1
 7. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
 9. the person who likes lavender is the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in july is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
