.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, cherry, grapes
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: techno, jazz, metal, hip-hop
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, scientific, mystery, martial-arts
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, ivory, emerald, purple
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, soy-milk, hot-chocolate
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of techno##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person eating apricot##1
 3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of metal##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the person who likes emerald is the fan of hip-hop##1
 6. the person eating cherry is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
 7. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the person watching crime movies is the person drinking tea##1
 9. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
10. the person eating grapes is the person who likes purple##1
11. the person who likes purple is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
12. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | asparagus    | grapes        | apricot        | cherry      |
| Music-Genre       | metal       | techno       | jazz      | hip-hop |
| Movie-Genre         | scientific | martial-arts | mystery | crime      |
| Color         | fuchsia          | purple         | ivory           | emerald    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk         | mirinda       | hot-chocolate     | tea   |

 